thread.title_full: Rosie O'Donnell's starting to look a lot like Steve Bannon | Washington Examiner

author: Anna Giaritelli
title: Rosie O'Donnell's starting to look a lot like Steve Bannon
text:
Actress and former talk host Rosie O'Donnell appears eager to step into her role portraying White House chief strategist Steve Bannon on NBC's "SNL" this Saturday .
The former "The View" host morphed a photo of her face onto Bannon's body and posted the finished image as her Twitter profile picture Thursday evening, just 48 hours before her NBC appearance.
O'Donnell strongly opposes President Trump and supported Hillary Clinton during the 2016 election.
